# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# IMPORTANT NOTES FOR DEVELOPERS
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
#
# NEVER COMMIT:
# ❌ .env files with real private keys
# ❌ Wallet keystore files
# ❌ Mnemonic phrases
# ❌ API keys or secrets
# ❌ Production deployment addresses (until public)
# ❌ Internal audit reports (until cleared)
#
# SAFE TO COMMIT:
# ✅ .env.example (template without secrets)
# ✅ Smart contract source code
# ✅ Test files
# ✅ Documentation
# ✅ Public audit reports
# ✅ Deployment scripts (without hardcoded keys)
# ✅ README and guides
